%e A074894 For n=27 Boman and Linusson give five examples of which the simplest is {-4,-1^{10},2^{16}} and its negative, where exponents denote repetitions. For n=486 Boman and Linusson give {-7,-4^{56},-1^{231},2^{176},5^{22}} and its negative.
